        "body": ">  This will only be efficient on the GPU for a small number of large groups (and slow for a large number of small groups).\r\n\r\nBut can be improved with multi-stream concurrency, which we plan to add in the future.\r\n\r\nIf we can use Numba to compile a (limited) filter syntax to PTX, we could apply this in parallel in a single kernel. How general are the filters that people want to run? Is it as broad as `apply()`?",
